# warnings

## COMMONJS_VARIABLE_IN_ESM

```text
[COMMONJS_VARIABLE_IN_ESM] The CommonJS `exports` variable is treated as a global variable in an ECMAScript module and may not work as expected
   в•ӯв”Җ[ cjs-in-esm.js:2:1 ]
   в”Ӯ
 1 в”Ӯ export let foo = 1
   в”Ӯ в”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җ  
   в”Ӯ    в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ This file is considered to be an ECMAScript module because of the `export` keyword here:
 2 в”Ӯ exports.foo = 2
   в”Ӯ в”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җ  
   в”Ӯ    в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ 
в”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ

```

